Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Barotac Viejo Central School in the Municipality of Barotac Viejo, Province of Iloilo, to Raul O. V. Causing Memorial Central School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 767
An Act Changing the Name of the Barotac Viejo Central School in the Municipality of Barotac Viejo, Province of Iloilo, to Raul O. V. Causing Memorial Central School
Section 1. The name of the Barotac Viejo Central School in the Municipality of Barotac Viejo, Province of Iloilo, is changed to Raul O. V. Causing Memorial School.1awphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
